00:11:34.720 --> 00:11:36.829
thank You, Lord, that these people would

00:11:36.839 --> 00:11:39.910
have a stirring

00:11:39.920 --> 00:11:43.710
and an urgency inside of them

00:11:43.720 --> 00:11:47.710
to get ready because Jesus is

00:11:47.720 --> 00:11:50.030
coming. We're excited about Your

00:11:50.040 --> 00:11:52.430
coming, Lord. We're excited about

00:11:52.440 --> 00:11:54.110
the signs of the

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:56.670
times and Your coming. We thank You, Lord,

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:58.430
for all that You're doing. We call

00:11:58.440 --> 00:12:01.550
healing, wholeness, and wellness over every

00:12:01.560 --> 00:12:03.509
single person represented here

00:12:03.519 --> 00:12:05.670
today. We call them delivered from

00:12:05.680 --> 00:12:07.590
sickness and disease from the top of

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:09.389
their heads to the soles of their

00:12:09.389 --> 00:12:09.399
feet—delivered

00:12:09.399 --> 00:12:12.030
from acid reflux, GERD, or whatever

00:12:12.040 --> 00:12:14.790
it may be. Jesus paid

00:12:14.800 --> 00:12:17.629
the price for you to walk in divine

00:12:17.639 --> 00:12:21.230
health over thyroid disorders,

00:12:21.240 --> 00:12:24.030
eating disorders, anorexia, and

00:12:24.040 --> 00:12:27.269
all kinds of things. God has paid the

00:12:27.279 --> 00:12:29.990
price for you to be free from it, and I

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:32.230
thank You, Lord, that You took it

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:34.030
all on the cross for them. I thank You,

00:12:34.040 --> 00:12:36.030
Father, that You bore it

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:37.910
in Your body so we need

00:12:37.920 --> 00:12:40.069
not bear it in our

00:12:40.069 --> 00:12:40.079
bodies.

00:12:40.079 --> 00:12:43.069
Jesus paid it for us. Father,

00:12:43.079 --> 00:12:45.230
I thank You for every person

00:12:45.240 --> 00:12:47.230
here who has liked,

00:12:47.240 --> 00:12:49.790
subscribed, and is helping me

00:12:49.800 --> 00:12:52.389
with the gospel.

00:12:52.399 --> 00:12:54.509
I call blessing

00:12:54.519 --> 00:12:57.750
on their house, family,

00:12:57.750 --> 00:12:57.760
and

00:12:57.760 --> 00:13:00.430
minds, and increase

00:13:00.430 --> 00:13:00.440
upon

00:13:00.440 --> 00:13:02.670
them in Jesus'name. They are the

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:04.389
head and not the tail, above and not

00:13:04.399 --> 00:13:06.350
beneath; they will go through and not

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:09.189
go under. They are more than

00:13:09.199 --> 00:13:11.949
conquerors through Him who is in

00:13:11.959 --> 00:13:14.670
Christ Jesus. We thank You, Lord, for

00:13:14.680 --> 00:13:16.110
Your covering,

00:13:16.120 --> 00:13:17.550
Your blood, and

00:13:17.560 --> 00:13:19.829
Your love

00:13:19.839 --> 00:13:24.350
for us. In Jesus'name, Amen. Well, I

00:13:24.360 --> 00:13:26.150
just want to say: please

00:13:26.160 --> 00:13:29.629
click that notification

00:13:29.639 --> 00:13:31.150
bell. I don't know where my pillows went,

00:13:31.150 --> 00:13:31.160
but

00:13:31.160 --> 00:13:32.509
it's fine; don't worry about

00:13:32.519 --> 00:13:36.110
them. Put a smile on your face and a song

00:13:36.120 --> 00:13:39.389
in your heart. Jesus loves you so much,

00:13:39.399 --> 00:13:42.350
and we love you. We will see you very

00:13:42.360 --> 00:13:44.910
soon. Have a blessed day.

00:13:44.920 --> 00:13:49.680
Bye-bye.

